# NEW WORKING CRISIS SYSTEM INTERFACE - UPDATED

This screenshot shows the NEW working crisis system interface with:
- Fixed demand changes based on disaster types (no longer stuck at 670)
- Dynamic subheadings that change with disaster selection
- Analytics panel with critical agents tracking
- Real-time demand updates based on disaster impact
- System health monitoring and optimization suggestions

DISASTER TYPES:
- Earthquake: Demand changes from 670 to ~750+
- Flood: Demand changes from 670 to ~720+
- Power Failure: Demand changes from 670 to ~730+
- Storm: Demand changes from 670 to ~700+

